<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Double P words pack a punch in Scrabble. Each P is worth 3 points, so PP contributes 6 points before you even count the rest of the word. With only 2 P tiles in the bag, holding both is rare — but when you do, these words will maximize your score.</p>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
