  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring PP Words</h2>

<p>These high-value PP words should be in every competitive player's vocabulary:</p>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
